name: The night sky on Mount Papandayan
description: Whether we realize it or not, the earth is getting worse with light pollution. It's hard to see the stars at night it's so beautiful and beautiful. It takes more effort to see it. We as humans must begin to realize the beauty we see must also be enjoyed by our future successors. The easiest step is to raise awareness if excess light is not good for the earth, many impacts can occur, especially for health. Let's control the light we use, for a better earth and future.
